    "body": "im using exactly this workaround for now but i have log js error in the console stating stuff like \n\n```\nUncaught Error: project_type is not a retrieved facet.\n```\n\nEdit: the error disappear actually now, not sure why\n\nhowever i tried to cleanup the widget array anyway before adding the new widget.\nIt seems that it is still possible to add widget after the start method\n\n``` javascript\ninstanceSearchHelper.setIndex(state.currentIndexName);\ninstantsearch.widgets.length = 0;\nstate.widgets.forEach(instanceSearch.addWidget, instanceSearch);\ninstanceSearchHelper.search();\n```\n",
